#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:3
msgid "Attachments"
msgstr "Ceangaltáin"

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:6
msgid "Sharing files in a chat"
msgstr "Comhaid a roinnt i gcomhrá"

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:8
msgid "You can share files in a chat in three ways."
msgstr "Is féidir leat comhaid a roinnt i gcomhrá ar thrí bhealach."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:10
msgid "First, you can simply drag'n'drop them on the chat."
msgstr ""
"Ar dtús, is féidir leat iad a tharraingt agus a scaoileadh ar an gcomhrá."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:15
msgid ""
"Second, you can select a file from your Nextcloud Files or a file manager by"
" choosing the little paperclip and selecting where you'd like to pick the "
"file from."
msgstr ""
"Ar an dara dul síos, is féidir leat comhad a roghnú ó do Nextcloud Files nó "
"ó bhainisteoir comhad tríd an ngearrthóg bheag páipéir a roghnú agus a "
"roghnú cá háit ar mhaith leat an comhad a roghnú."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can add more files until you are done and decide to share the files. You"
" can also add a text caption to your shared files, providing a brief "
"description or context."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat tuilleadh comhad a chur leis go dtí go mbeidh tú críochnaithe"
" agus go gcinnfidh tú na comhaid a roinnt. Is féidir leat fotheideal téacs a"
" chur le do chomhaid chomhroinnte freisin, ag soláthar cur síos gairid nó "
"comhthéacs."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:28
msgid ""
"All users will be able to click the files to view, edit or download them, "
"irrespective of them having a user account. Users with an account will have "
"the file automatically shared with them while external guest users will get "
"them shared as a public link."
msgstr ""
"Beidh gach úsáideoir in ann cliceáil ar na comhaid chun iad a fheiceáil, a "
"chur in eagar nó a íoslódáil, is cuma má tá cuntas úsáideora acu nó nach "
"bhfuil. Roinnfear an comhad go huathoibríoch le húsáideoirí a bhfuil cuntas "
"acu agus roinnfear é mar nasc poiblí le húsáideoirí aoi seachtracha."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:34
msgid "Polls in chat"
msgstr "Pobalbhreitheanna sa chomhrá"

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:36
msgid ""
"You can create a poll in groups chats from the new message additional "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat pobalbhreith a chruthú i gcomhráite grúpa ón teachtaireacht "
"nua le gníomhartha breise."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:41
msgid "A poll has two settings:"
msgstr "Tá dhá shocrú ag pobalbhreith:"

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:43
msgid ""
"**Anonymous polls**: Participants cannot see who voted for which option."
msgstr ""
"**Pobalbhreitheanna gan ainm**: Ní féidir le rannpháirtithe a fheiceáil cé a"
" vótáil ar son rogha ar leith."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:44
msgid ""
"**Allow multiple choices**: Participants can select more than one option."
msgstr ""
"**Ceadaigh roghanna iolracha**: Is féidir le rannpháirtithe níos mó ná rogha"
" amháin a roghnú."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:46
msgid ""
"You can also import polls for auto-fill and export polls as JSON files to "
"save them locally."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat pobalbhreitheanna a allmhairiú freisin le haghaidh uathlíonta"
" agus pobalbhreitheanna a onnmhairiú mar chomhaid JSON chun iad a shábháil "
"go háitiúil."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:51
msgid "You can close a poll from the poll dialog."
msgstr "Is féidir leat pobalbhreith a dhúnadh ón dialóg pobalbhreithe."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:56
msgid ""
"As a moderator, you can create the poll directly or you can save it as a "
"draft to edit it later."
msgstr ""
"Mar mhodhnóir, is féidir leat an pobalbhreith a chruthú go díreach nó is "
"féidir leat í a shábháil mar dhréacht le cur in eagar níos déanaí."

#: ../../talk/attachments.rst:61
msgid ""
"You can find poll drafts in ``Shared items`` tab or next to the poll title "
"input field."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat dréachtaí pobalbhreithe a fháil sa chluaisín ``Míreanna "
"Comhroinnte`` nó in aice leis an réimse ionchuir teidil pobalbhreithe."
